"- CAPTCHA Solver (C)\n"
"- Audio Transcription (A)\n"
"- Smart Dictation (S)\n"
"- Announce Status (I)\n"
"- Label Object (L)\n"
"- Manage/Scan Labels (Shift+L)\n"
"- UI Explorer (E)\n"
"- AI Operator (Shift+A)\n"
"- Check Update (U)\n"
"- Recall Last Result (Space)\n"
"- Commands Help (H)\n"
"- Open Settings (Alt+S)\n"
"- Report Quota Exhausted Keys (Alt+Q)\n"
"- Report Advanced Routing (Alt+M)"
